msgctxt "mn103:6.11"
msgid "Māyasmanto vivādaṃ āpajjitthā’ti. "
msgstr "Please don’t get into a fight about this.’ "

msgctxt "mn103:6.12"
msgid "Iti duggahitaṃ duggahitato dhāretabbaṃ, suggahitaṃ suggahitato dhāretabbaṃ. "
msgstr "So you should remember what has been incorrectly memorized as incorrectly memorized and what has been correctly memorized as correctly memorized. "

msgctxt "mn103:6.13"
msgid "Duggahitaṃ duggahitato dhāretvā suggahitaṃ suggahitato dhāretvā yo dhammo yo vinayo so bhāsitabbo. "
msgstr "Remembering this, you should speak on the teaching and the training. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: nya7, sc5
msgctxt "mn103:7.1"
msgid "Tatra ce tumhākaṃ evamassa: "
msgstr "Now, you might think, "

