msgid "Tadamināpetaṃ āyasmanto jānātha—"
msgstr "But the venerables should know that this is how "

msgctxt "mn103:7.11"
msgid "yathā atthato hi kho sameti, byañjanato nānaṃ. "
msgstr "such agreement on the meaning and disagreement on the phrasing comes to be. "

msgctxt "mn103:7.12"
