msgid "Suggahitaṃ suggahitato dhāretvā duggahitaṃ duggahitato dhāretvā yo dhammo yo vinayo so bhāsitabbo. "
msgstr "Remembering this, you should speak on the teaching and the training. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: nya8, pts-vp-pli2.241, sc6
msgctxt "mn103:8.1"
msgid "Tatra ce tumhākaṃ evamassa: "
msgstr "Now, you might think, "

msgctxt "mn103:8.2"
msgid "‘imesaṃ kho āyasmantānaṃ atthato ceva sameti byañjanato ca sametī’ti, tattha yaṃ bhikkhuṃ suvacataraṃ maññeyyātha so upasaṅkamitvā evamassa vacanīyo: "
